      "side": 1,
      "message": "I am not a fan of relying on the existence of issues on Gerrit or Rietveld and being dependent on their uptime for tests run on our bots. This is why I was skipping the test in the old location. But maybe ok for now, lets revisit this if the test ends up being flaky.",
