        "id": 5015
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-10-06T13:15:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "+1, if buildbucket goes down, or if it \"forgets\" about this CL, we\u0027re going to run into failures. It\u0027s becoming clear to me that we need three modes for tests: always run, skip on local presubmit, only run in manual mode.",
